t-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8edc8e2d-511b-431a-ad79-3b147843458a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c21-ced7-11ef-82e0-c76413fdd4bf\" style=\"color:#555555;\">음식점을 가면</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-19d43e86-9da0-4731-8705-08f42e5ac785\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c22-ced7-11ef-82e0-45c3eb2524f5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">각 테이블에 고객의 의견을 듣는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-8fe17628-1a4f-4439-945f-209926d5198e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca54c23-ced7-11ef-82e0-8d82f3b83e76\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>메모지 같은</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c24-ced7-11ef-82e0-1fc289ac5a89\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 것을</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-63a4dce2-f375-402c-99f7-925e9ea560b2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c25-ced7-11ef-82e0-3dedd9ec1c03\" style=\"color:#555555;\">보신 적이 있으실 겁니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-915e8339-98c5-4e80-b730-db1dec3a0793\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c26-ced7-11ef-82e0-f3281c90c9c5\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-4b44ae20-ac97-4faf-acdd-040bfc07243b\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c27-ced7-11ef-82e0-4d84022d6dc0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이것은 고객의 의견을 조사하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f4fb81df-5c54-40e3-9716-c500474bdee5\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca54c28-ced7-11ef-82e0-0d9fde5dfe4d\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>설문지 형식의</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c29-ced7-11ef-82e0-cd898cf44f71\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 페이퍼이고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-88b8755f-c5a3-4c46-8c5e-bf5ba8edc8da\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c2a-ced7-11ef-82e0-09dde120f511\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이 설문의 의견을 듣고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6de0812c-84e5-4393-9e09-be99ab0e688c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c2b-ced7-11ef-82e0-4dde537a8d07\" style=\"color:#555555;\">정책이나 서비스에 반영하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-dcbd5a86-1acb-42cd-965b-3424333b0848\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c2c-ced7-11ef-82e0-9dedf7abe7c3\" style=\"color:#555555;\">경우가 많습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a22a3345-2ed3-4f00-9e7d-c1e028032cf2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c2d-ced7-11ef-82e0-0b89d0b3af9f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-5c3a98a5-dabe-447a-8508-82f4612d2bc2\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c2e-ced7-11ef-82e0-4319d2174df1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">물론 요즘은 온라인 툴이나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a94dcb96-aa5a-420f-8371-078052eeeb31\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c2f-ced7-11ef-82e0-cd86ea6c28c9\" style=\"color:#555555;\">구글 폼 등으로 설문을 받지만</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b0dce001-cd45-4891-8778-dbf96fef82c1\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c30-ced7-11ef-82e0-554bc2042ba6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">종이의 향수에 젖어 오프라인으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-d9b29bca-fff9-469f-9385-d831ae9b4df8\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c31-ced7-11ef-82e0-335aaf759b41\" style=\"color:#555555;\">수기로 적고 응모하는</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-445cad9e-1779-4048-acfa-03b4ff648f1c\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c32-ced7-11ef-82e0-b1ec3ded8910\" style=\"color:#555555;\">형태도 많이 봐 왔습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-7175018c-2a7c-468b-a03f-f91755dc2419\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c33-ced7-11ef-82e0-3b50931f3133\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-15135ac7-0063-4afb-9c57-7de42eb8a982\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c34-ced7-11ef-82e0-6b0f196b6cc0\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이는 온라인에 익숙하지 않은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-b11cc7da-871f-48d3-8f22-985235f6514d\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c35-ced7-11ef-82e0-db9f6f95e828\" style=\"color:#555555;\">나이 많은 어르신분들이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c566d154-32a3-46a8-ac3d-4cec0d48ba40\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c36-ced7-11ef-82e0-23f9fe21f0fd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">즐겨 찾는 매장이나</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-2945e7be-9c21-4f8f-b6d7-721aeafb7486\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c37-ced7-11ef-82e0-2b909e5cd8fa\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주 고객층의 연령이 높은</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-a6dfa71d-9f1b-4926-bf46-f309b45ef819\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca54c38-ced7-11ef-82e0-4b2e09c3ce15\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그런 식당에서</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-6d70854a-14b0-4c62-9143-49c644290d10\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca57349-ced7-11ef-82e0-e7e3e884a85c\" style=\"color:#555555;\">주로 이러한 방법으로</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-fc8814ae-d6f3-4aa6-b384-d624fc7fbe03\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id