0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca59a73-ced7-11ef-82e0-75740a90d908\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>디자인 유무</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a74-ced7-11ef-82e0-bf715f5777a8\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 또는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca59a75-ced7-11ef-82e0-83e6f8b5e8c2\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>배송방법</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a76-ced7-11ef-82e0-8f72aa1c8c9f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-550e5a18-1be2-4709-9083-8989b815a65e\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a77-ced7-11ef-82e0-0d70e0c7a2d1\" style=\"color:#555555;\">그리고 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca59a78-ced7-11ef-82e0-7b460c1891a9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타 옵션 등을</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a79-ced7-11ef-82e0-716d77603193\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 물어 보고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-c04bc657-301c-4c17-bd0b-fecd09fe0a33\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a7a-ced7-11ef-82e0-25ae7d408664\" style=\"color:#555555;\">결정하게 됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-14aeb74e-5411-4e90-9799-a2e58925c441\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a7b-ced7-11ef-82e0-3f5ba1033275\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-66a93102-5c5e-4940-94b8-23269cdfb1d6\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a7c-ced7-11ef-82e0-a9713edff826\" style=\"color:#555555;\">디자인이 걸린 시간은</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca59a7d-ced7-11ef-82e0-9f1795f3dfca\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b> 8시간</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a7e-ced7-11ef-82e0-c3b9a5f6a244\" style=\"color:#555555;\">입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f826ca93-a463-4ebf-9952-06df1e9ece57\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a7f-ced7-11ef-82e0-99350bd7c896\" style=\"color:#555555;\">이후 컨펌 과정을 거쳐</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-849f57ce-8d00-4f65-8088-b66d55263e38\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a80-ced7-11ef-82e0-41924d78c813\" style=\"color:#555555;\">확정하는데 단 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca59a81-ced7-11ef-82e0-61aee565306a\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>하루 만에</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a82-ced7-11ef-82e0-6fa7ab28da8f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> 작업이</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-ce570835-24ae-4dce-9bb8-0f3d75d32a0f\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca59a83-ced7-11ef-82e0-d3ec9595c35b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">완료되었습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-3533f4bf-269c-44ff-8879-445aa3530478\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c094-ced7-11ef-82e0-db4e16450cee\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-wrappingParagraph se-l-inner-left\" id=\"SE-81c4191d-5b02-464c-b248-65523a4c3fb1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-component-slot se-component-slot-float\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223720442176/004.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component-slot\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-823d580b-9509-4859-88a6-82c93d10de6a\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c095-ced7-11ef-82e0-c94c59ef9805\" style=\"color:#555555;\">여기서 주의해야 할 사항이 있습니다. 고객님께서 100g의 모조 계열로 작업을 요청하였습니다만 인쇄 경험상 100g은 너무 얇아 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c096-ced7-11ef-82e0-55c336fb0dc8\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#b0f1ff;\">톰슨 작업이 뜯김이나 깔끔하게 제작되지 않을 경우를 염려</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c097-ced7-11ef-82e0-d11e23a1d431\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하여 저희는 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c098-ced7-11ef-82e0-69d5a82f0714\" style=\"color:#555555;background-color:#b0f1ff;\">한 단계 평량을 올린 120g으로 제작</span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c099-ced7-11ef-82e0-a3183a793023\" style=\"color:#555555;\">해 드렸습니다. 물론 지인의 거래처라서 무상으로 작업해 드렸으며 더 깔끔한 인쇄물을 위해 고객님도 컨펌을 해 주셔서 안전하게 납품될 수 있었습니다. 이처럼 인쇄는 여러 가지 변수가 존재합니다. 반드시 인쇄 전문가와 상의하여 제작하시기 바랍니다. 그렇지 않으면 사고가 날 수 있는 것이 또한 인쇄 작업입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-talktalk se-l-default\" id=\"SE-1418b90c-befd-4fc1-8b9e-69500b0bf9bc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-talktalk se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n\n<span class=\"se-talktalk-banner-text\">\n<span class=\"se-blind\">궁금할 땐 네이버 톡톡하세요!</span>\n</span>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-93ca3e1e-d347-40b0-a3dc-8a5e35dbb025\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" style=\"max-width:473px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link-use se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223720442176/005.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7867dde3-f36b-496e-9f3a-62f101a14ed4\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-default se-section-align-center\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dc4108f6-175f-4ad1-a723-07bb455bdfa6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-f39bf444-2c0c-4366-a323-5f23582947aa\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c09a-ced7-11ef-82e0-f11ae00e6ae6\" style=\"color:#555555;\">다음 글에는 실제로 제작된 물건을 가지고</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-bc57ec2e-111d-4652-9fe3-7e6ca4e439e0\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c09b-ced7-11ef-82e0-efd732a38577\" style=\"color:#555555;\">자세하게 설명해 드리겠습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-22fde2a4-df76-40a7-8a72-6a6cfa35f494\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi se-weight-unset\" id=\"SE-cca5c09c-ced7-11ef-82e0-cb8aa2115e57\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center\" id=\"SE-66f22c74-ecb0-400f-8991-e2b327c78060\" style=\"line-height:2.0;\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-cca5c09d-ced7-11ef-82e0-81af73487bce\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>리플렛 이미지 모음</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-9ce43bdd-652f-45f0-b8cd-6c0ef543ec7b\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/papascompany/Printguide@d608cd58b294f3de28c0892f4733cfb9fb9cec62/223720442176/006.png\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-item\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\